ession_ratio": 1.4696356275303644, "no_speech_prob": 0.21323758363723755}, {"id": 22, "seek": 7700, "start": 102.0, "end": 105.0, "text": " Nada puede estar más lejos de la verdad.", "tokens": [51614, 40992, 8919, 8755, 3573, 476, 19136, 368, 635, 13692, 13, 51764], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07309033735743109, "compression_ratio": 1.4696356275303644, "no_speech_prob": 0.21323758363723755}, {"id": 23, "seek": 10500, "start": 105.0, "end": 110.0, "text": " Es una frente a los argentinos que pretenden apropiarse de este resultado.", "tokens": [50364, 2313, 2002, 19873, 257, 1750, 33977, 15220, 631, 1162, 8896, 1882, 1513, 9448, 405, 368, 4065, 28047, 13, 50614], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12702222580605366, "compression_ratio": 1.5695067264573992, "no_speech_prob": 0.03033156506717205}, {"id": 24, "seek": 10500, "start": 110.0, "end": 114.0, "text": " Es importante que todos tengamos algo en claro.", "tokens": [50614, 2313, 9416, 631, 6321, 10370, 2151, 8655, 465, 16742, 13, 50814], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12702222580605366, "compression_ratio": 1.5695067264573992, "no_speech_prob": 0.03033156506717205}, {"id": 25, "seek": 10500, "start": 114.0, "end": 119.0, "text": " Estos personajes de nuestro pasado nos sumieron en una aventura suicida", "tokens": [50814, 4410, 329, 43960, 368, 14726, 24794, 3269, 2408, 14440, 465, 2002, 36399, 2991, 28419, 2887, 51064], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12702222580605366, "compression_ratio": 1.5695067264573992, "no_speech_prob": 0.03033156506717205}, {"id": 26, "seek": 10500, "start": 119.0, "end": 123.0, "text": " que nos podría haber costado todo, mucho más de lo que está el país", "tokens": [51064, 631, 3269, 27246, 15811, 2063, 1573, 5149, 11, 9824, 3573, 368, 450, 631, 3192, 806, 10572, 51264], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12702222580605366, "compression_ratio": 1.5695067264573992, "no_speech_prob": 0.03033156506717205}, {"id": 27, "seek": 10500, "start": 123.0, "end": 130.0, "text": " en condiciones de pagar y nos podría haber dejado CINI-PF y con un Estado fundido.", "tokens": [51264, 465, 45960, 368, 28024, 288, 3269, 27246, 15811, 21259, 1573, 383, 1464, 40, 12, 47, 37, 288, 416, 517, 29740, 2374, 2925, 13, 51614], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12702222580605366, "compression_ratio": 1.5695067264573992, "no_speech_prob": 0.03033156506717205}, {"id": 28, "seek": 13000, "start": 130.0, "end": 135.0, "text": " Porque repito, un fallo adverso en este juicio le habría costado al país", "tokens": [50364, 11287, 1085, 3528, 11, 517, 2100, 78, 614, 331, 539, 465, 4065, 3649, 18322, 476, 32794, 2686, 2063, 1573, 419, 10572, 50614], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07181339770291759, "compression_ratio": 1.5272727272727273, "no_speech_prob": 0.025216033682227135}, {"id": 29, "seek": 13000, "start": 135.0, "end": 139.0, "text": " a todos nosotros 18.000 millones de dólares.", "tokens": [50614, 257, 6321, 13863, 2443, 13, 1360, 22416, 368, 32596, 13, 50814], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07181339770291759, "compression_ratio": 1.5272727272727273, "no_speech_prob": 0.025216033682227135}, {"id": 30, "seek": 13000, "start": 139.0, "end": 143.0, "text": " Tener que pagarlos habría representado un enorme obstáculo", "tokens": [50814, 314, 7971, 631, 11812, 39734, 32794, 2686, 2906, 1573, 517, 33648, 9579, 842, 25436, 51014], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07181339770291759, "compression_ratio": 1.5272727272727273, "no_speech_prob": 0.025216033682227135}, {"id": 31, "seek": 13000, "start": 143.0, "end": 146.0, "text": " en el camino de nuestra recuperación económica.", "tokens": [51014, 465, 806, 34124, 368, 16825, 25692, 3482, 33537, 2262, 13, 51164], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07181339770291759, "compression_ratio": 1.5272727272727273, "no_speech_prob": 0.025216033682227135}, {"id": 32, "seek": 13000, "start": 146.0, "end": 150.0, "text": " Además, es importante considerar el precio inconmensurable", "tokens": [51164, 34621, 11, 785, 9416, 1949, 289, 806, 46916, 20972, 76, 694, 25863, 51364], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07181339770291759, "compression_ratio": 1.5272727272727273, "no_speech_prob": 0.025216033682227135}, {"id": 33, "seek": 13000, "start": 150.0, "end": 153.0, "text": " que la Argentina pagó por esta irresponsabilidad", "tokens": [51364, 631, 635, 18336, 11812, 812, 1515, 5283, 38626, 5177, 4580, 51514], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07181339770291759, "compression_ratio": 1.5272727272727273, "no_speech_prob": 0.025216033682227135}, {"id": 34, "seek": 13000, "start": 153.0, "end": 159.0, "text": " en términos de riesgo país, tasa de interés y menor crecimiento económico.", "tokens": [51514, 465, 45198, 329, 368, 23932, 1571, 10572, 11, 8023, 64, 368, 728, 2191, 288, 26343, 31668, 14007, 33537, 2789, 13, 51814], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.07181339770291759, "compression_ratio": 1.5272727272727273, "no_speech_prob": 0.025216033682227135}, {"id": 35, "seek": 15900, "start": 160.0, "end": 163.0, "text": " Independientemente de la pericia legal de nuestro equipo,", "tokens": [50414, 21809, 1196, 16288, 368, 635, 680, 15341, 5089, 368, 14726, 30048, 11, 50564], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08191807516689958, "compression_ratio": 1.463302752293578, "no_speech_prob": 0.0013215253129601479}, {"id": 36, "seek": 15900, "start": 163.0, "end": 165.0, "text": " hay una verdad irrefutable.", "tokens": [50564, 4842, 2002, 13692, 16014, 69, 32148, 13, 50664], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08191807516689958, "compression_ratio": 1.463302752293578, "no_speech_prob": 0.0013215253129601479}, {"id": 37, "seek": 15900, "start": 165.0, "end": 170.0, "text": " Expropiar está mal, porque robar está mal.", "tokens": [50664, 21391, 1513, 9448, 3192, 2806, 11, 4021, 3870, 289, 3192, 2806, 13, 50914], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08191807516689958, "compression_ratio": 1.463302752293578, "no_speech_prob": 0.0013215253129601479}, {"id": 38, "seek": 15900, "start": 170.0, "end": 176.0, "text": " Y quebrar este principio nos costó aproximadamente 12 años de falta de inversiones", "tokens": [50914, 398, 631, 30280, 4065, 34308, 3269, 2063, 812, 48892, 2272, 11424, 368, 22111, 368, 21378, 5411, 51214], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08191807516689958, "compression_ratio": 1.463302752293578, "no_speech_prob": 0.0013215253129601479}, {"id": 39, "seek": 15900, "start": 176.0, "end": 178.0, "text": " por culpa del juicio en curso.", "tokens": [51214, 1515, 44870, 1103, 3649, 18322, 465, 31085, 13, 51314], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08191807516689958, "compression_ratio": 1.463302752293578, "no_speech_prob": 0.0013215253129601479}, {"id": 40, "seek": 15900, "start": 178.0, "end": 185.0, "text": " Es decir, menos empresas, menos trabajo, más pobreza y más indigencia.", "tokens": [51314, 2313, 10235, 11, 8902, 26433, 11, 8902, 18099, 11, 3573, 40819, 2394, 288, 3573, 1016, 3213, 2755, 13, 51664], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08191807516689958, "compression_ratio": 1.463302752293578, "no_speech_prob": 0.0013215253129601479}, {"id": 41, "seek": 18500, "start": 186.0, "end": 191.0, "text": " Entonces, el populismo puede aparentar ser beneficioso en el corto plazo", "tokens": [50414, 15097, 11, 806, 24017, 6882, 8919, 1882, 1898, 289, 816, 10304, 23540, 465, 806, 11278, 78, 499, 29722, 50664], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06158412663282546, "compression_ratio": 1.6016260162601625, "no_speech_prob": 0.002344971988350153}, {"id": 42, "seek": 18500, "start": 191.0, "end": 193.0, "text": " y quedar bien frente a las cámaras,", "tokens": [50664, 288, 39244, 3610, 19873, 257, 2439, 6476, 6209, 296, 11, 50764], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06158412663282546, "compression_ratio": 1.6016260162601625, "no_speech_prob": 0.002344971988350153}, {"id": 43, "seek": 18500, "start": 193.0, "end": 196.0, "text": " pero le envía señales al resto del mundo", "tokens": [50764, 4768, 476, 2267, 2686, 13830, 4229, 419, 28247, 1103, 7968, 50914], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06158412663282546, "compression_ratio": 1.6016260162601625, "no_speech_prob": 0.002344971988350153}, {"id": 44, "seek": 18500, "start": 196.0, "end": 200.0, "text": " y trae consecuencias negativas en el mediano y largo plazo.", "tokens": [50914, 288, 944, 68, 40526, 7801, 12046, 2485, 35725, 465, 806, 1205, 6254, 288, 31245, 499, 29722, 13, 51114], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06158412663282546, "compression_ratio": 1.6016260162601625, "no_speech_prob": 0.002344971988350153}, {"id": 45, "seek": 18500, "start": 200.0, "end": 204.0, "text": " Porque ponen jaque los cimientos legales sobre los que se sustentan", "tokens": [51114, 11287, 9224, 268, 2784, 1077, 1750, 269, 34841, 1676, 4229, 5473, 1750, 631, 369, 5402, 317, 282, 51314], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06158412663282546, "compression_ratio": 1.6016260162601625, "no_speech_prob": 0.002344971988350153}, {"id": 46, "seek": 18500, "start": 204.0, "end": 208.0, "text": " todas las inversiones en el país, especialmente las estratégicas", "tokens": [51314, 10906, 2439, 21378, 5411, 465, 806, 10572, 11, 41546, 2439, 46603, 9150, 51514], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06158412663282546, "compression_ratio": 1.6016260162601625, "no_speech_prob": 0.002344971988350153}, {"id": 47, "seek": 18500, "start": 208.0, "end": 212.0, "text": " que se realizan con una mirada de largo plazo.", "tokens": [51514, 631, 369, 22828, 282, 416, 2002, 3149, 1538, 368, 31245, 499, 29722, 13, 51714], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06158412663282546, "compression_ratio": 1.6016260162601625, "no_speech_prob": 0.002344971988350153}, {"id": 48, "seek": 21200, "start": 213.0, "end": 217.0, "text": " Que se entienda, para todos lo que se llenan la boca hablando de soberanía", "tokens": [50414, 4493, 369, 948, 30498, 11, 1690, 6321, 450, 631, 369, 4849, 45008, 635, 34624, 29369, 368, 26212, 282, 2686, 50614], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08016470626548484, "compression_ratio": 1.6081632653061224, "no_speech_prob": 0.0015274061588570476}, {"id": 49, "seek": 21200, "start": 217.0, "end": 222.0, "text": " y del desarrollo de los sectores estratégicos y del interés nacional.", "tokens": [50614, 288, 1103, 38295, 368, 1750, 22610, 2706, 46603, 9940, 288, 1103, 728, 2191, 29836, 13, 50864], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08016470626548484, "compression_ratio": 1.6081632653061224, "no_speech_prob": 0.0015274061588570476}, {"id": 50, "seek": 21200, "start": 222.0, "end": 225.0, "text": " La mejor forma de defender los intereses estratégicos", "tokens": [50864, 2369, 11479, 8366, 368, 26537, 1750, 20157, 279, 46603, 9940, 51014], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08016470626548484, "compression_ratio": 1.6081632653061224, "no_speech_prob": 0.0015274061588570476}, {"id": 51, "seek": 21200, "start": 225.0, "end": 229.0, "text": " es con inversiones cuantiosas y sostenida en el tiempo.", "tokens": [51014, 785, 416, 21378, 5411, 2702, 394, 2717, 296, 288, 262, 18946, 2887, 465, 806, 11772, 13, 51214], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08016470626548484, "compression_ratio": 1.6081632653061224, "no_speech_prob": 0.0015274061588570476}, {"id": 52, "seek": 21200, "start": 229.0, "end": 234.0, "text": " Y la única forma de garantizarla es con seguridad jurídica.", "tokens": [51214, 398, 635, 30104, 8366, 368, 22251, 9736, 875, 785, 416, 35415, 12721, 24455, 2262, 13, 51464], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08016470626548484, "compression_ratio": 1.6081632653061224, "no_speech_prob": 0.0015274061588570476}, {"id": 53, "seek": 21200, "start": 234.0, "end": 240.0, "text": " Esto es el verdadero patriotismo, no el nacionalismo barato de pacotilla.", "tokens": [51464, 20880, 785, 806, 13692, 2032, 44210, 6882, 11, 572, 806, 29836, 6882, 2159, 2513, 368, 15165, 310, 5291, 13, 51764], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08016470626548484, "compression_ratio": 1.6081632653061224, "no_speech_prob": 0.0015274061588570476}, {"id": 54, "seek": 24000, "start": 241.0, "end": 244.0, "text": " En adoptar el modelo opuesto, los falsos soberanistas", "tokens": [50414, 2193, 6878, 289, 806, 27825, 999, 22057, 11, 1750, 16720, 329, 26212, 282, 14858, 50564], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06858772088673488, "compression_ratio": 1.7302904564315353, "no_speech_prob": 0.000837340485304594}, {"id": 55, "seek": 24000, "start": 244.0, "end": 248.0, "text": " pusieron a todos los argentinos en riesgo y los empobrecieron.", "tokens": [50564, 31252, 14440, 257, 6321, 1750, 33977, 15220, 465, 23932, 1571, 288, 1750, 4012, 996, 3326, 16308, 13, 50764], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06858772088673488, "compression_ratio": 1.7302904564315353, "no_speech_prob": 0.000837340485304594}, {"id": 56, "seek": 24000, "start": 248.0, "end": 252.0, "text": " El juicio de YPF comenzó durante la presidencia de Cristina Kirchner.", "tokens": [50764, 2699, 3649, 18322, 368, 398, 47, 37, 29564, 812, 14427, 635, 1183, 4380, 2755, 368, 23199, 1426, 11305, 339, 1193, 13, 50964], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06858772088673488, "compression_ratio": 1.7302904564315353, "no_speech_prob": 0.000837340485304594}, {"id": 57, "seek": 24000, "start": 252.0, "end": 255.0, "text": " Luego, el juicio se perdió en primera instancia", "tokens": [50964, 45665, 11, 806, 3649, 18322, 369, 680, 4504, 812, 465, 17382, 1058, 22862, 51114], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06858772088673488, "compression_ratio": 1.7302904564315353, "no_speech_prob": 0.000837340485304594}, {"id": 58, "seek": 24000, "start": 255.0, "end": 258.0, "text": " durante la presidencia de Alberto Fernández.", "tokens": [51114, 14427, 635, 1183, 4380, 2755, 368, 45709, 16675, 18606, 4371, 13, 51264], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06858772088673488, "compression_ratio": 1.7302904564315353, "no_speech_prob": 0.000837340485304594}, {"id": 59, "seek": 24000, "start": 258.0, "end": 264.0, "text": " Ahora, la Argentina logró una sentencia histórica en esta administración.", "tokens": [51264, 18840, 11, 635, 18336, 31013, 812, 2002, 2279, 10974, 33196, 15192, 465, 5283, 9737, 3482, 13, 51564], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06858772088673488, "compression_ratio": 1.7302904564315353, "no_speech_prob": 0.000837340485304594}, {"id": 60, "seek": 24000, "start": 264.0, "end": 269.0, "text": " Repito, una sentencia histórica en esta administración.", "tokens": [51564, 3696, 3528, 11, 2002, 2279, 10974, 33196, 15192, 465, 5283, 9737, 3482, 13, 51814], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06858772088673488, "compression_ratio": 1.7302904564315353, "no_speech_prob": 0.000837340485304594}, {"id": 61, "seek": 26900, "start": 269.0, "end": 274.0, "text": " Lo que parecía imposible, nosotros lo hicimos posible.", "tokens": [50364, 6130, 631, 7448, 31298, 38396, 964, 11, 13863, 450, 23697, 8372, 26644, 13, 50614], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10201130291022877, "compression_ratio": 1.5780590717299579, "no_speech_prob": 0.017735140398144722}, {"id": 62, "seek": 26900, "start": 274.0, "end": 277.0, "text": " Ellos apostaron con nuestro futuro.", "tokens": [50614, 8353, 329, 19484, 6372, 416, 14726, 23953, 13, 50764], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10201130291022877, "compression_ratio": 1.5780590717299579, "no_speech_prob": 0.017735140398144722}, {"id": 63, "seek": 26900, "start": 277.0, "end": 282.0, "text": " Nosotros no apostamos, nosotros simplemente ganamos.", "tokens": [50764, 18749, 11792, 572, 19484, 2151, 11, 13863, 33190, 7574, 2151, 13, 51014], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10201130291022877, "compression_ratio": 1.5780590717299579, "no_speech_prob": 0.017735140398144722}, {"id": 64, "seek": 26900, "start": 282.0, "end": 287.0, "text": " Esta administración una vez más levantó los platos rotos,", "tokens": [51014, 20547, 9737, 3482, 2002, 5715, 3573, 30612, 812, 1750, 3403, 329, 4297, 329, 11, 51264], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10201130291022877, "compression_ratio": 1.5780590717299579, "no_speech_prob": 0.017735140398144722}, {"id": 65, "seek": 26900, "start": 287.0, "end": 291.0, "text": " porque el liberalismo es hacernos cargo de los errores del pasado", "tokens": [51264, 4021, 806, 13767, 6882, 785, 46093, 1248, 329, 19449, 368, 1750, 45935, 495, 1103, 24794, 51464], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10201130291022877, "compression_ratio": 1.5780590717299579, "no_speech_prob": 0.017735140398144722}, {"id": 66, "seek": 26900, "start": 291.0, "end": 294.0, "text": " y hacernos cargo también de las necesidades del futuro.", "tokens": [51464, 288, 46093, 1248, 329, 19449, 6407, 368, 2439, 11909, 10284, 1103, 23953, 13, 51614], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10201130291022877, "compression_ratio": 1.5780590717299579, "no_speech_prob": 0.017735140398144722}, {"id": 67, "seek": 26900, "start": 294.0, "end": 297.0, "text": " Por eso hemos enviado al Congreso un proyecto", "tokens": [51614, 5269, 7287, 15396, 2267, 72, 1573, 419, 4280, 38021, 517, 32285, 51764], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10201130291022877, "compression_ratio": 1.5780590717299579, "no_speech_prob": 0.017735140398144722}, {"id": 68, "seek": 29700, "start": 297.0, "end": 300.0, "text": " para modificar la ley de expropiaciones,", "tokens": [50364, 1690, 1072, 25625, 635, 27786, 368, 1278, 1513, 72, 9188, 11, 50514], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08270403870150574, "compression_ratio": 1.58984375, "no_speech_prob": 0.01914694905281067}, {"id": 69, "seek": 29700, "start": 300.0, "end": 304.0, "text": " para que la arrogancia de la política no nos vuelva a costar otra década perdida,", "tokens": [50514, 1690, 631, 635, 594, 340, 1275, 2755, 368, 635, 25029, 572, 3269, 20126, 2757, 257, 2063, 289, 13623, 9198, 1538, 12611, 2887, 11, 50714], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08270403870150574, "compression_ratio": 1.58984375, "no_speech_prob": 0.01914694905281067}, {"id": 70, "seek": 29700, "start": 304.0, "end": 310.0, "text": " y para que nunca más la propiedad privada pueda ser puesta en tela de juicio en nuestro país.", "tokens": [50714, 288, 1690, 631, 13768, 3573, 635, 2365, 1091, 345, 2915, 1538, 31907, 816, 2362, 7841, 465, 29203, 368, 3649, 18322, 465, 14726, 10572, 13, 51014], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08270403870150574, "compression_ratio": 1.58984375, "no_speech_prob": 0.01914694905281067}, {"id": 71, "seek": 29700, "start": 310.0, "end": 316.0, "text": " Y también quisiera aclarar algo, para que no haya lugar a confusiones.", "tokens": [51014, 398, 6407, 37945, 10609, 696, 2200, 289, 8655, 11, 1690, 631, 572, 24693, 11467, 257, 1497, 301, 5411, 13, 51314], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08270403870150574, "compression_ratio": 1.58984375, "no_speech_prob": 0.01914694905281067}, {"id": 72, "seek": 29700, "start": 316.0, "end": 321.0, "text": " El hecho de que nosotros estemos arreglando el desastre que nos dejaron", "tokens": [51314, 2699, 13064, 368, 631, 13863, 871, 4485, 594, 3375, 16201, 806, 730, 49199, 631, 3269, 21259, 6372, 51564], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08270403870150574, "compression_ratio": 1.58984375, "no_speech_prob": 0.01914694905281067}, {"id": 73, "seek": 29700, "start": 321.0, "end": 324.0, "text": " no significa, bajo ningún punto de vista,", "tokens": [51564, 572, 19957, 11, 30139, 30394, 14326, 368, 22553, 11, 51714], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08270403870150574, "compression_ratio": 1.58984375, "no_speech_prob": 0.01914694905281067}, {"id": 74, "seek": 32400, "start": 324.0, "end": 330.0, "text": " que tal desastre no existiera y todo lo sabemos muy bien.", "tokens": [50364, 631, 4023, 730, 49199, 572, 2514, 10609, 288, 5149, 450, 27200, 5323, 3610, 13, 50664], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05500144850124012, "compression_ratio": 1.5633802816901408, "no_speech_prob": 0.011792723089456558}, {"id": 75, "seek": 32400, "start": 330.0, "end": 335.0, "text": " La virtud de nuestros equipos no nos puede hacer olvidar la impericia del pasado,", "tokens": [50664, 2369, 4480, 532, 368, 24099, 5037, 329, 572, 3269, 8919, 6720, 43194, 289, 635, 10100, 15341, 1103, 24794, 11, 50914], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05500144850124012, "compression_ratio": 1.5633802816901408, "no_speech_prob": 0.011792723089456558}, {"id": 76, "seek": 32400, "start": 335.0, "end": 341.0, "text": " porque si eso ocurre estaremos condenados a repetir los mismos errores.", "tokens": [50914, 4021, 1511, 7287, 26430, 265, 871, 23118, 416, 1556, 4181, 257, 13645, 347, 1750, 47458, 45935, 495, 13, 51214], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05500144850124012, "compression_ratio": 1.5633802816901408, "no_speech_prob": 0.011792723089456558}, {"id": 77, "seek": 32400, "start": 341.0, "end": 346.0, "text": " Por eso quiero brindar algunos reconocimientos individuales.", "tokens": [51214, 5269, 7287, 16811, 738, 471, 289, 21078, 43838, 34841, 2609, 279, 13, 51464], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05500144850124012, "compression_ratio": 1.5633802816901408, "no_speech_prob": 0.011792723089456558}, {"id": 78, "seek": 32400, "start": 346.0, "end": 350.0, "text": " Este logro es consecuencia del trabajo riguroso, profesional", "tokens": [51464, 16105, 3565, 340, 785, 40526, 47377, 1103, 18099, 8329, 8977, 78, 11, 42882, 51664], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05500144850124012, "compression_ratio": 1.5633802816901408, "no_speech_prob": 0.011792723089456558}, {"id": 79, "seek": 35000, "start": 350.0, "end": 353.0, "text": " y compartido del equipo jurídico del Estado,", "tokens": [50364, 288, 18113, 2925, 1103, 30048, 12721, 24455, 2789, 1103, 29740, 11, 50514], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.18675006669143152, "compression_ratio": 1.448, "no_speech_prob": 0.6129090785980225}, {"id": 80, "seek": 35000, "start": 353.0, "end": 358.0, "text": " conducido por la Secretaria Legal y Técnica y Cerebro Jurídico de esta gestión,", "tokens": [50514, 45095, 2925, 